### Created
- **`packages/learning-engine/src/progress/AIProgressReviewService.ts`** — Service that aggregates user study data for a date range. Uses `ProgressService`, `WeaknessDetectionService`, and `AnalyticsService` internally. Methods:
  - `generateReview(input, startDate, endDate)` — filters all study data by date range, computes summary stats, skill progress, weakness report, vocabulary status, progress trend, recommendations, and tutor feedback
  - `computeVocabularyStatus` — counts vocab by status (new/learning/reviewing/mastered)
  - `determineProgressTrend` — rates overall trend from skill-level trends
  - `generateRecommendations` / `generateTutorFeedback` — rule-based suggestions and tutor-style commentary
    
- **`packages/learning-engine/src/progress/__tests__/AIProgressReviewService.test.ts`** — 7 unit tests covering: complete review output, empty date range, date filtering, vocabulary status, study summary totals, tutor feedback, and recommendations from weakness data

### Modified
- **`packages/learning-engine/src/types.ts`** — Added `AIProgressReviewInput`, `AIProgressReviewSummary`, and `AIProgressReviewData` interfaces
- **`packages/learning-engine/src/progress/index.ts`** — Exported `AIProgressReviewService`

### Test results
7/7 passing (the only failure is a pre-existing `DailyPlanService` test unrelated to these changes).
